  \defgroup Chrono Chrono

  \brief Hardware clock access and time-measurement utilities.
*/

/*!
  \namespace toy::chrono

  \brief Time-measurement types: duration and time-point aliases over \c std::chrono.

  Thin wrappers that keep engine code free of direct \c std::chrono qualification while preserving full interoperability
  with the standard library. All members are transparent aliases; no additional runtime behavior is introduced.
*/

